e things, Holo saunters in with quite the feast.\n\nThis is a VR Animation of Spice and Wolf: Spring Log, sequel to the original Spice and Wolf VR animation.\nThe game has a 30 minute story and a game mode where you can watch part of the anime alongside its characters in the style of Japanese paper street theater.\nA peaceful life in the bathhouse with wolfgirls awaits.\n", "short_description": "The team behind the original series has gotten together to bring you into the world of Spice and Wolf again for a second installment of VR animation! \nAnimation has evolved from \"watching\" to \"experiencing.\""}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Oculus_Icon_mobile.png", "id": "4977285745675565", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974887_4977285749008898_4482133498831970937_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LWni38TAXzoQ7kNvgFwe7qC&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC2nSm3eMyD-S_N2s4m0ZdcKD8Xvp9B0WPaZyrMRU7uJw&oe=6714FE7B"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Portrait_en.png", "id": "1115593388914444", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031366_1115593392247777_1108929082473903627_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hZQEz2xmMWcQ7kNvgH-FlYg&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD4gwqxGnoBSQZkGQMESLUFfI_dL73XU6O3yaj3BDRVsQ&oe=6714D484"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Hero_en.png", "id": "871157030095923", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982668_871157033429256_6789488157395094913_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mfO0tuDWkiMQ7kNvgEMLf3c&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDW4zsL_AG3RiHrOSLZxlwEru_nlvrwXPD25ku2SZxvyg&oe=6714F850"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Square_en.png", "id": "477446693254143", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974841_477446696587476_4659881486425096962_n.png?_nc_cat